82%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%25A7%2581%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2588%2591%25E4%25BA%258B%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%258E%25A7%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E9%259D%259E%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E5%259B%25B0%25E9%259B%25A3&h=c8a285db\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190623/s00001/1561298824098/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E6%9B%BE%E5%81%A5%E8%B6%85-%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%BA%E5%88%91%E4%BA%8B%E6%AA%A2%E6%8E%A7%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E9%9D%9E%E5%B8%B8%E5%9B%B0%E9%9B%A3</a><br />\n<br />\n於2014年佔領運動期間遭七警毆打及襲警的曾健超在集會上發言稱，「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">小市民要私人刑事檢控警察是非常困難</span></strong>」，提醒市民如有警方涉濫暴的證據，不要急於在網上發布，待適當時候於法庭公開。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T08:54:06.000Z","msg":"咁如果係告其他市民刑事呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T09:33:44.000Z","msg":"可以。<br />\n<br />\n根據普通法，任何人都享有同律政司司長相同嘅權利，提出刑事檢控。當年上議院法官Lord Wilberforce 就曾經形容私人檢控係<strong>「<span style=\"color: purple;\">針對權力機關怠慢或偏袒的一項寶貴的憲法保障</span>」</strong><strong>（a valuable constitutional safeguard against inertia or partiality on the part of authority)</strong><br />\n<br />\n任何人都可以根據普通法或者裁判官條例第14條提出私人檢控。如果裁判官接納，會向被告發出傳票。<br />\n<br />\n不過有一點要留意，係一個私人檢控案入面，律政司係可以隨時介入取代原檢控人嘅身份，再決定是否繼續有關法律程序，或者撤銷控罪既。"},{"pid":"1a3d1ca17efa5d10bf36169139c08bcfe80b8b19","tid":1306681,"uid":264591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c9d0c3fb884d5fc7c7513433c83c4c579e5b930","tid":1306681,"uid":277586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d42983c21e4a5b74281319a29dd7af78acb7e0db","tid":1306681,"uid":6609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7484cc8612da54013be1825309400b8ea796048","tid":1306681,"uid":266410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T08:52:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190623/s00001/1561298824098/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E6%9B%BE%E5%81%A5%E8%B6%85-%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%9